    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m selling my reliable ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it to get you where you need to go comfortably. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is just waiting for its next adventure! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
