    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a fantastic blend of reliability and style. The exterior presents beautifully, showcasing a vibrant paint finish that has been regularly waxed, with only minor road wear visible upon close inspection. Inside, the interior remains remarkably clean; the seats are supportive and free of tears, and all dashboard controls operate with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine runs strong and quiet, benefited by a documented history of on-time oil changes and recent brake service. It handles the road with confidence, providing a smooth, rattle-free ride. This is a dependable, well-cared-for example perfect for someone seeking quality and longevity.",
      "price": 33850.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
