      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for reliability and performance. Featuring a clean history and well-preserved interior, it offers a turn-key solution for the discerning driver seeking value without compromise. We invite you to experience the superior handling and refined engineering of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 36500.0,
