    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic deal on a car that still has so much life left in it. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
