      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement. Critically, this example has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability these M-cars are known for. Recent valve clearance adjustments ensure the valvetrain operates at peak efficiency. A performance-oriented specimen ready for the apex.",
